            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/php9a9wt4.jpg?VersionId=.C1hfsLPHhMuwQQcmSdTmtrguhEAxbcW&amp;itok=SJegH6R0" title="赖清德星期三在就职记者会上对两岸关系提出看法。他认为，台湾已是独立的国家，没有再宣布台湾独立的必要。（自由时报）" alt="赖清德星期三在就职记者会上对两岸关系提出看法。他认为，台湾已是独立的国家，没有再宣布台湾独立的必要。（自由时报）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2023-01/php9a9wt4.jpg?VersionId=.C1hfsLPHhMuwQQcmSdTmtrguhEAxbcW&amp;itok=SJegH6R0" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
